  "diagram_type": "C4Context",
  "code": "%% C4 Context diagram: System-level view showing external actors and systems\n%% This is the highest zoom level in the C4 model\n%% Shows who uses the system and what external systems it depends on\n\nC4Context\n    title Internet Banking System - Context\n\n    %% People who interact with the system\n    Person(customer, \"Banking Customer\", \"Views account balances and makes payments\")\n    Person(support, \"Support Staff\", \"Handles customer queries\")\n\n    %% The system under design\n    System(bankingSystem, \"Internet Banking System\", \"Allows customers to manage accounts online\")\n\n    %% External systems the banking system depends on\n    System_Ext(emailSystem, \"Email System\", \"Sends transactional emails\")\n    System_Ext(coreBank, \"Core Banking System\", \"Stores account and transaction data\")\n\n    %% Relationships between actors and systems\n    Rel(customer, bankingSystem, \"Uses\", \"HTTPS\")\n    Rel(support, bankingSystem, \"Administers\", \"HTTPS\")\n    Rel(bankingSystem, emailSystem, \"Sends emails via\", \"SMTP\")\n    Rel(bankingSystem, coreBank, \"Reads/writes accounts\", \"REST API\")",
